properties.Name: EducationAttainmentLevel
properties.Description:
The level of educational attainment achieved by the Individual.

Ex:
-  Less than 9th Grade
-  9th to 12th Grade
-  High School Graduate 
-  High School Equivalency Graduate
-  Some College, No Degree
-  Associate Degree
-  Bachelor's Degree
-  Graduate Degree
-  Professional Degree

Note:
This must be an identifying relationship since one or more degrees may be granted at a single time and one or more degrees may be achieved from the same educational institution.
